examples.en: Someday I'd like to travel abroad.
Let's have lunch someday next week.
We hope to someday own our own home.
She hopes to publish her novel someday.
I would like to visit Rome someday.
Someday you will understand my actions.
He hopes, someday, to have his own business.
He dreams of someday possessing great wealth.
You may kill someone someday with your raw power.
A small-town girl who hopes to become a somebody someday.
Their incautious behavior is going to get them into trouble someday.
The deportee vowed that he would someday return to a liberated nation.
A promising writer who just may write the great American novel someday.
